<div id="review_1245486124" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1245486124" />
    <a title="Night0vvl" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/30529990-night0vvl"><img alt="Night0vvl" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1523807996p2/30529990.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1245486124?book_show_action=true">Apr 04, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Night0vvl" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Night0vvl" href="/user/show/30529990-night0vvl">Night0vvl</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1245486124" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9214809334258674307">There&apos;s only one thing I can say about John Christopher&apos;s works, they are awesome! And if he decided not to share his imagination with us the world would have missed so much </span>
  <span id="freeText9214809334258674307" style="display:none">There's only one thing I can say about John Christopher's works, they are awesome! And if he decided not to share his imagination with us the world would have missed so much </span>
